lead_paragraph: Robert Lewandowski scored both goals as runaway leaders Bayern Munich coasted to a predictable 2-0 win at home to relegation-threatened Hoffenheim in the Bundesliga on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Bayern Coast Home Against Hoffenheim With Lewandowski Brace
